// {type:sequence}
[User}]pressButton>[class Keyboard]
[User]-[note:User presses any button]
[class Keyboard]callback(Pressed)>>[class Radio]
[class Keyboard]-[note:Keyboard informs via previously registered callbacks]
[class Radio]sendUpdate>[class XPlaneReceiver]
[class Radio]-[note:In case a mode change occured, the radio will inform the remote x-plane instance about a change of a DataRef]
[class XPlaneReceiver]UDP("DREF")>[x-plane]
[x-plane]UDP("RREF mode").>[class XPlaneReceiver]
[x-plane]-[note:In case it is configured, the XPlaneReceiver can react on the 'reflected' mode changes.]